06d6a345?u=3D16283549], Peter [https://substack.com/redirect/6fce0499-3ab6-=
4592-8da8-a9200eb4d22d?u=3D16283549], and the Circle team for working with =
me on this piece, and to Dan [https://substack.com/redirect/e486b91c-9eac-4=
80d-a38d-2bf13414e098?u=3D16283549] for editing!
That=E2=80=99s all for today! See you back here tomorrow for some Weekly Op=
timism.=20
Thanks for Reading, Packy

