em;"><em><span>The </span><strong>crucial test</strong><span> that any stab=
lecoin must pass for the market to actually trust it is: </span><strong>if =
a user wants to redeem their stablecoins for genuine dollars, under any rea=
sonable circumstance, can they do so?</strong></em></p></blockquote><p styl=
e=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;=
"><span>&#8220;Reasonable&#8221; is doing a lot of work here. People should=
 </span><em>always</em><span> be able to redeem their stablecoins for genui=
