0;"><strong>Cryptocurrency-Backed</strong></p></li><li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 4px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><p style=3D"c=
olor: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom=
: 0;"><strong>Algorithmic</strong></p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a;=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>We&#8217;ll =
