ike UST, aren&#8217;t backed by dollars, a basket of cryptos, commodities, =
or anything, really, outside of what they create themselves.&#160;</span></=
p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 1em 0;"><span>Instead of explaining this insanity myself, I&#8217;ll tur=
n it over to the </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/927ea9bc-1=
