text-decoration: underline;">inimitable Matt Levine</a><span>:</span></p><p=
 style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1=
em 0;"><em>Here is how an algorithmic stablecoin works:</em></p><ol style=
=3D"margin-top: 0;"><li style=3D"margin-bottom: 4px; margin-left: 8px; marg=
in-right: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><em>You wake up one morni=
ng and invent two crypto tokens.</em></p></li><li style=3D"margin-bottom: 4=
px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><p style=3D"color:=
 #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"=
><em>One of them is the stablecoin, which I will call &#8220;Terra,&#8221; =
