-bottom: 4px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 4px;"><p style=
=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-b=
ottom: 0;"><em>You try to find people to buy them.</em></p></li><li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 4px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 4px;=
"><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
; margin-bottom: 0;"><em>Luna will trade at some price determined by supply=
