=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-b=
ottom: 0;"><em>Terra should trade at $1. If it trades above $1, people &#82=
12; arbitrageurs &#8212; can buy $1 worth of Luna for $1 and exchange them =
for one Terra worth more than a dollar, for an instant profit. If it trades=
 below $1, people can buy one Terra for less than a dollar and exchange it =
for $1 worth of Luna, for an instant profit. These arbitrage trades push th=
